# Business Domain Rules

## Quotation Status Flow

```
draft -> sent -> accepted / rejected / expired
```

- New quotations MUST start as `draft`
- Only `draft` quotations can be edited (update/delete items)
- `sent` quotations are immutable — create a new version to modify
- Every status transition MUST create a `QuotationHistory` record

## Pricing Rules

- All monetary values are stored as **integers** (no floating point)
- Default currency: VND (Vietnamese Dong)
- Supported currencies: VND, USD
- `unitPrice` * `quantity` = line item total
- Quotation total = sum of all line item totals (before tax/discount)

## Entity Relations

```
Customer (1) ---> (N) Quotation
Quotation (1) ---> (N) QuotationItem
Quotation (1) ---> (N) QuotationHistory
```

- Deleting a Customer: soft-delete only (preserve quotation history)
- Deleting a Quotation: cascade delete its items and history
- Products are independent catalog items — not linked to quotation items by FK

## History Actions

Valid `action` values for `QuotationHistory`:

| Action | Trigger |
|--------|---------|
| `created` | New quotation created |
| `updated` | Quotation fields modified |
| `status_changed` | Status transition |
| `ai_extracted` | AI successfully extracted data from document |
| `ingestion_failed` | AI extraction failed |
| `email_sent` | Quotation delivered via email |
| `item_added` | Line item added |
| `item_removed` | Line item removed |
